{"tid":891323,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【寄生蟲上腦】吞鼻涕蟲致癱捱咗8年 澳28歲男併發症離世","createTime":"2018-11-06T04:23:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-10T03:16:17.000Z","uid":130626,"like":181,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":101,"replies":[{"pid":"089fe7703c5caacd71c901e586010b936060f4bc","tid":891323,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T04:23:28.000Z","msg":"澳洲悉尼一名男子8年前在派對上吞食「鼻涕蟲」後，寄生蟲入侵腦部，導致下半身癱瘓，上周五因為併發症離世。<br />\n事發在2010年，當時19歲的巴拉德（Sam Ballard）和朋友開派對玩鬥大膽遊戲時吞下一隻蛞蝓（鼻涕蟲），其後身體不適求醫，醫生證實他腦部已受寄生蟲「廣東住血線蟲」（angiostrongylus cantonensis）感染，隨後更患上嗜酸細胞性腦膜腦炎（eosinophilic meningo-encephalitis），昏迷臥床長達420天。<br />\n本是前途大好的欖球員，巴拉德留醫3年終於出院，但半身不遂，需以輪椅代步及靠喉管餵食，亦未能如常控制自己的行為。他的母親凱蒂（Katie）曾在社交網站上撰文，形容該次意外「破壞和永遠改變了他的人生，也永遠改變了我的人生」，又稱希望兒子日後能恢復步行能力，可惜至他離世，願望仍然落空。<br />\n巴拉德臨終前對不離不棄照顧他的凱蒂說「我愛妳」。<br />\n廣東住血線蟲主要寄生在老鼠體內，因此亦被稱為「鼠肺蟲」（rat lungworm），但若蝸牛及蛞蝓等生物吃下老鼠的排泄物，均可能受這種寄生蟲感染。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181106/large/1541436830_78f3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181106%2Flarge%2F1541436830_78f3.jpg&h=be37179f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181106/58879275\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181106%2F58879275&d=%2FAH5SopbTphPa9NB3QF7xaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=ba52bdb7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181106%2F58879275&h=5f7f9d48\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181106/58879275</a>"},{"pid":"9e5906afddb4db89bb18132f758f7dfb44159619","tid":891323,"uid":139967,"like":228,"dislike":55,"score":173,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T04:27:23.000Z","msg":"抵死"},{"pid":"f27de9e4ea2bbde65a6ba9be929930cfa1b6a2f9","tid":891323,"uid":121473,"like":12,"dislike":12,"score"